data.description: Welcome home to this amazing 3-bedroom, 2 full bath home in the Dover community. Upon walking into the home, you will immediately fall in love with the oversized large porch with a porch swing that draws you in to take in the beautiful neighborhood. The family room is directly connected to the large open concept kitchen with granite countertops, tons of storage and a butcher block island. On the first floor you have a full bathroom and 2 bedrooms. On the second floor you have an expansive master suite with an oversized bedroom, two separate walk-in closets with a private bathroom with a jacuzzi tub, two separate vanity sinks and shower. There is a small deck off of the master suite as well, perfect for that morning coffee while just waking up from your bedroom overlooking the back yard. The backyard has a completely fenced in with a built-in fireplace. The seller has redone the steps in the front and back, extended the driveway and added the carport to the side of the garage. This home is one of a kind! Book your personal showing with your favorite realtor ASAP or join us for the open house on Sunday 11-26 from 2-4 by Dustin Pringle.
